    RedirectFlowService

    public static final class RedirectFlowService.RedirectFlowCreateRequest
extends PostRequest<RedirectFlow>

    Request class for RedirectFlowService.create().

    Creates a redirect flow object which can then be used to redirect your customer to the GoCardless Pro hosted payment pages.

        public RedirectFlowService.RedirectFlowCreateRequest withScheme(RedirectFlowService.RedirectFlowCreateRequest.Scheme scheme)

        The Direct Debit scheme of the mandate. If specified, the payment pages will only allow the set-up of a mandate for the specified scheme.

      • withSessionToken

        public RedirectFlowService.RedirectFlowCreateRequest withSessionToken(String sessionToken)

        The customer’s session ID must be provided when the redirect flow is set up and again when it is completed. This allows integrators to ensure that the user who was originally sent to the GoCardless payment pages is the one who has completed them.
